{"tid":2350434,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有女仔 同我講佢鍾意Trae Young 我會同佢講...","createTime":"2021-01-02T09:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T12:08:24.000Z","uid":11294,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1720a058a67914d48bec7677b282ee7a88f99768","tid":2350434,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">我會話..<br />\n鍾意得好，請你繼續鐘意。 </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">Let Go Hawks</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人同我講，佢鍾意Luka Doncic，<br />\n我會講..<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">有Taste</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人同我講，<br />\n佢鍾意「My boy」（Shaqtin&rsquo; A Fool MVP），<br />\n我會話...<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">識揀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人同我講，佢好鍾意高比拜仁，<br />\n我會講..<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我都係佢一直嘅Fans。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人同我講 ，佢鍾意嘅球星，冇戒指，<br />\n我會講...<br />\n<span class=\"red\">請你繼續支持佢，請為佢加油。</span><br />\n<br />\n但有如果有人同我講，<br />\nNBA已死，我會講。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">希望今年嘅所有新人，會比到曙光你。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">最後  MVP同 Finals MVP <br />\n唔係最好波嘅獎。<br />\n只要唔係黑哨就要撐。</span><br />\n<br />\n最最後你仲係勒邦占士嘅fans，我會講。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">屌你老母你啲taste真係好撚曳。</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad09b5dbe9b3cf667f1caa2c4ef4f644da2d9709","tid":2350434,"uid":11294,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">Let Go Hawks</span></span>"},{"pid":"0dbacf32b4f53189c147f9df3d9977dbac1da4a9","tid":2350434,"uid":67197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"依家已經無人叫佢FOJ"},{"pid":"ac3c56354008eed8da92650df7fb82bf03a79795","tid":2350434,"uid":313334,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T10:05:05.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"ac2daade6331d29afa6229b8c8df0c846c547620","tid":2350434,"uid":132189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0